code: public static void assertContainsWWWAuthenticateHeader(ElasticsearchSecurityException e) {     assertThat(e.status(), is(RestStatus.UNAUTHORIZED)).     assertThat(e.getHeaderKeys(), hasSize(1)).     assertThat(e.getHeader("WWW-Authenticate"), notNullValue()).     assertThat(e.getHeader("WWW-Authenticate"), contains("Basic realm=\"" + XPackField.SECURITY + "\" charset=\"UTF-8\"")). }
